{"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SimpleAction\/onNotifyName(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyName"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO15SimpleActionRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SimpleActionRef","text":"SimpleActionRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyName"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"handler"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This represents the underlying ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::name"},{"type":"text","text":" signal"}]}],"style":"note","name":"Note"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/simpleaction\/onnotifyname(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GIO","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyName","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"text":"SimpleActionRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO15SimpleActionRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"title":"onNotifyName(flags:handler:)","externalID":"s:3GIO20SimpleActionProtocolPAAE12onNotifyName5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bC3RefV_AG09ParamSpecN0VtctF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO12SimpleActionC"},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text